sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant CLI
  participant G as Gateway
  participant V as vLLM
  U->>CLI: prompt
  CLI->>G: chat (tools)
  G->>V: forward
  V-->>G: tool_call(read,...)
  G-->>CLI: tool_call
  CLI->>CLI: run read
  CLI->>G: tool_result
  G->>V: continue
  V-->>G: final
  G-->>CLI: final
